{"tid":587243,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"認真 如果想入讀獸醫有咩途徑可行?","createTime":"2018-03-10T09:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T18:17:15.000Z","uid":3775,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fe8d03bf4865d0d27a0d0f9a0b9466fdda559cf6","tid":587243,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T09:16:42.000Z","msg":"先講下自己背景先<br />\n<br />\n小弟就24了 CityU 畢業  Chem grad 2Up hon啦<br />\n<br />\nAL EE CC<br />\n<br />\n咁中學成績不堪入目既<br />\n<br />\n但係呢 自己一直有個夢想係做獸醫....<br />\n<br />\n如果 再考DSE 係唔係要返夜校重讀? 因為要SBA <br />\n<br />\n定係考GCE ALEVEL? <br />\n<br />\n定有其他國家會睇我大學既成績同activity? 淨係考返好英文就夠?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我返左工年半 我一直質疑自己 什麼是happy life 究竟係想搵錢? 究竟係想有精神上既滿足?<br />\n<br />\n我好想係我 老之前搏一次 唔想其他 生活壓到機會都無既時候流眼淚"},{"pid":"e104e923842ecfa35f7f16d69937609c994cbdee","tid":587243,"uid":3775,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T09:21:23.000Z","msg":"就算它日再乞食我都唔會後悔<br />\n<br />\n我真係想好鍾意動物... 好想識照顧動物 好想識多D醫學<br />\n<br />\n如果係要考試 我就備戰去考<br />\n<br />\n如果係要錢 我就努力D 儲....<br />\n<br />\n但真係想知有咩好既途徑做...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9171812324f74a19d9ab5950199e073f5ad92a","tid":587243,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T10:18:19.000Z","msg":"矛人知<br />\n<br />\n我都係買阿仙奴做到4弟算了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d4f0790a982371d91e602374834470f2959757","tid":587243,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T10:19:20.000Z","msg":"讀asso走後門入"},{"pid":"4e02bfa5df875cb000bb8ae3224edea5e208ee57","tid":587243,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05d4f0790a982371d91e602374834470f2959757","tid":587243,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T10:19:20.000Z","msg":"讀asso走後門入"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T10:19:47.000Z","msg":"asso 點走後門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 