sg":"自己搵下啦 伸手到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"我緊係有搵啦...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但未考過DSE 又未考過GCG ALEVEL<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知考咩先好..."},{"pid":"303c2f46afe1d9c1835e0ef5ad7c0922db54d29a","tid":587243,"uid":172506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:37:02.000Z","msg":"AL讀過相關科目 可以自修 免sba"},{"pid":"31b8688e86586bd85033c7d11ccd0e67164329dd","tid":587243,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"303c2f46afe1d9c1835e0ef5ad7c0922db54d29a","tid":587243,"uid":172506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:37:02.000Z","msg":"AL讀過相關科目 可以自修 免sba"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T14:38:13.000Z","msg":"真?<br />\n<br />\n咁考DSE 好過<br />\n<br />\n屈下BIO CHEM先... 計下數 不過怕中文同通識///"},{"pid":"7cf181eaaeb37d44606bad55f044bfb40e542f94","tid":587243,"uid":172506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>AL讀過相關科目 可以自修 免sba</blockquote>真?<br />\n<br />\n咁考DSE 好過<br />\n<br />\n屈下BIO CHEM先... 計下數 不過怕中文同通識///</blockquote><br />\n考過AL唔代表可以不戰而勝 <br />\nDse下乜科都咁撚淺 講題型同小心 <br />\n要花時間同心機操練熟悉度同速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外中文<br />\n其實就係強化版左少少既ce中文（新制）<br />\n係oral同綜合改左出題風格 但肯留意下近年pp就掌握到<br />\n通識反而係講字速大於一切既科 <br />\n做漏一細題已經可以gg <br />\n題目可以靠操+做靚個表達/組織 唔好1999<br />\n就唔會爛龜<br />\n<br />\n不過你考dse做咩 <br />\n有獸醫prog係要dse?"},{"pid":"016768638c8e46085af2a33ace3643c978ca8693","tid":587243,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T00:23:42.000Z","msg":"我就覺得無咩可能<br />\n你不如退而求其次做獸醫助護<br />\n鍾意動物唔代表一定要做獸醫，做助護都幫到動物<br />\n<br />\n我識人都係大學畢業之後走咗去做<br />\n<a href=\"http://hknursejobs.com/search.php?tagid=2073\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhknursejobs.com%2Fsearch.php%3Ftagid%3D2073&d=7TsPuvTwDarcJYwxYOrhW5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=21c41096\" target=\"_blank\">http://hknursejobs.com/search.php?tagid=2073</a>"},{"pid":"ca6dece4e4ff07c068b22f194e88cba966c1c852","tid":587243,"uid":3775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7cf181eaaeb37d44606bad55f044bfb40e542f94","tid":587243,"uid":172506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>AL讀過相關科目 可以自修 免sba</blockquote>真?<br />\n<br />\n咁考DSE 好過<br />\n<br />\n屈下BIO CHEM先... 計下數 不過怕中文同通識///</blockquote><br />\n考過AL唔代表可以不戰而勝 <br />\nDse下乜科都咁撚淺 講題型同小心 <br />\n要花時間同心機操練熟悉度同速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外中文<br />\n其實就係強化版左少少既ce中文（新制）<br />\n係oral同綜合改左出題風格 但肯留意下近年pp就掌握到<br />\n通識反而係講字速大於一切既科 <br />\n做漏一細題已經可以gg <br />\n題目可以靠操+做靚個表達/組織 唔好1999<br />\n就唔會爛龜<br />\n<br />\n不過你考dse做咩 <br />\n有獸醫prog係要dse?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T02:51:49.000Z","msg":"我留意左 台灣收生計分方式 佢聯合招收 唔會限年份 但唔可以dse 又al咁用<br />\n<br />\n至於cityu新開既一定要<br />\n<br />\n澳美英 我就無乜研究 但第一樣要考好ielts 先<br />\n<br />\nAll bands 7 我諗我會刷ielts先 我差writing oral就做到<br />\n<br />\nDse我唔會裸考 如果係考 我應該辭職 搵私補 瘋狂讀書背書 爆上去"},{"pid":"7807d27244a3648874cfe458a9fcca54bcec52b7","tid":587243,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:33:37.000Z","msg":"Thx 大家意建<br />\n<br />\n我諗我會比兩年自己試<br />\n<br />\n第一步應考ielts 考夠7為止<br />\n<br />\n同時搵埋外國大學 可能做下衰仔向家人求借錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （覺得好虧欠左咁）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同時報dse考 bio chem<br />\n<br />\n第二年 考中英數加通識 睇下有冇機啦"},{"pid":"dd8664523f1aa5abd601a8505c117bd87e78a1ff","tid":587243,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:42:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1fb44b090af6a5edef5ce4288ac957d7938341a","tid":587243,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd8664523f1aa5abd601a8505c117bd87e78a1ff","tid":587243,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:42:09.